{"tid":1350255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【焦土要瞄準核心】捉緊機會，全民一次過向新鴻基/政府/牛屎佬復仇","createTime":"2019-07-22T12:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T13:06:31.000Z","uid":242437,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d5298c06f45c92caecfcde14a8cad52f9e3f67d3","tid":1350255,"uid":242437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:22:16.000Z","msg":"眾所周知屯門一帶係+發展左幾十年嘅重點新市鎮<br />\n最近呢幾年亦都有<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大量嘅新樓盤</span>落成<br />\n當中我發現有唔少就同新鴻基有關 背後嘅資金來源都好紅<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">呢啲新樓盤除咗係重要嘅政府同地產商直接收入，亦都會影響未來區域性嘅樓市發展</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下做咗少少資料蒐集<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mYjF4kK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmYjF4kK.png&h=aa5aca68&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Drenyd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrenyd5.png&h=de338826&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZdxkjT7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZdxkjT7.png&h=249525d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5LDzpkO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5LDzpkO.png&h=d74b7217&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UkjKMy9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUkjKMy9.png&h=f87bd7c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先當然係今次事故關聯既yoho一帶！<br />\n有無諗過點解新界嘅牛屎佬由以前一文不值嘅農民世家，俾人捧到而家係丁權王子、圍村王子？<br />\n<br />\n因為由港英政府開始已經想駐守新界西北發展；地皮發展潛力更加自然升值，佢哋就雞犬升天！<br />\n所以要一次過向三權報仇，就要由經濟方面落手！<br />\n今日只不過係網絡流傳既幾張對話內容、話會劈友，已經可以癱瘓屯門元朗天水圍各大小商場行業。當小商家撤出、大財團停頓，成個社區就真係critical hit！<br />\n所以：<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">以後凡係有咩風吹草動，或者故意挑選某啲重要日子，大家文宣一齊網絡集體攻勢扮fact checked，將件事扣上黑社會的帽子，話黑社會準備日光日白劈友開拖，就已經足以不少程度上令元朗屯門一帶變成死城。</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n固然呢個方法唔濫用，否則就會變成輪迴。但係只要有一兩次好似尋晚咁嘅事件，已經足以將我哋嘅謊言延續一段不短的時間。<br />\n當<span style=\"color: red;\">以訛傳訛、風聲鶴唳嘅方法亦都可以輔助以正面出擊，好似沙田新城市廣場嘅手足一樣，主動集體投訴、癱瘓附近嘅商場、政府機構</span>，而且用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反對黑勢力擾亂民生作為旗幟</span></span>！<br />\n只要將件事推起，長期放上枱面，附近一帶嘅樓價係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定會跌</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n想像一下因爲<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">鄉黑官警問題令到樓價大跌、成個新界北地區發展停頓，會係幾恐怖</span></span></span></strong>，變成美國嘅底特津⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">大家參考facebook各假藍絲專頁</span>，領悟下！<br />\n我個人認為絕對唔可以咁做。"},{"pid":"5b7d01a1652eaa16584298212bb6c28aea5b0108","tid":1350255,"uid":242437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:23:11.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"31e5f8ceec913d6d274baaff3d1bd8dd0956e648","tid":1350255,"uid":242437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:31:19.000Z","msg":"負評係地產商留既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b16d767e0becd704d22781c780311d85c9a224","tid":1350255,"uid":242437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:06:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1550169/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-%E6%94%BE%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E6%B0%B4%E7%9B%A1%E9%B5%9D%E9%A3%9B-%E9%85%92%E6%A8%93%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86-%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%96%E5%87%BA%E5%84%BC%E5%A6%82%E6%AD%BB%E5%9F%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1550169%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B-%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%259B%25A1%25E9%25B5%259D%25E9%25A3%259B-%25E9%2585%2592%25E6%25A8%2593%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%2590%2586-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2584%25BC%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259F%258E&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHsjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=0810f1ad\" dat